[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/06/90690.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1215830","time":"2017-2-24 23:40","userId":"wattlebird","userName":"Genius、小乖🌟💯","userSign":"(Enjoy your (real) life!)","message":"BFS","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/41/264146.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1215832","time":"2017-2-24 23:42","userId":"264146","userName":"小T","userSign":"","message":"百度了一下：宽度（/广度）优先搜索算法？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/06/90690.jpg","floor":"#2-2","id":"1215838","time":"2017-2-24 23:46","userId":"wattlebird","userName":"Genius、小乖🌟💯","userSign":"","message":"如果运行两遍 BFS 就可以算出全 BGM 距离最为遥远的两个人。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/30/133075.jpg","floor":"#2-3","id":"1215846","time":"2017-2-24 23:52","userId":"liaune","userName":"君寻","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Genius、小乖</span> 说: 如果运行两遍 BFS 就可以算出全 BGM 距离最为遥远的两个人。</q></div>两遍？正向和逆向吗？<br>不太能捋顺这中间的结构呀"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/06/90690.jpg","floor":"#2-4","id":"1215850","time":"2017-2-24 23:55","userId":"wattlebird","userName":"Genius、小乖🌟💯","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">君寻</span> 说: 两遍？正向和逆向吗？<br>不太能捋顺这中间的结构呀</q></div><a href=\"http://wattlebird.github.io/2014/09/21/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://wattlebird.github.io/2014/09/21/</a>树的直径/"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/17/78/177820.jpg","floor":"#2-5","id":"1215872","time":"2017-2-25 02:07","userId":"franklinyu","userName":"Franklin Yu","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Genius、小乖</span> 说: http://wattlebird.github.io/2014/09/21/树的直径/</q></div>兩次 BFS 是「相距最遠的兩個人」，樓主說的是「離你最遠的人」，所以一次 BFS（或者任何 search）就夠了<br><br>另外地址是 <a href=\"http://wattlebird.github.io/2014/09/21/%E6%A0%91%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%B4%E5%BE%84/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://wattlebird.github.io/2014 ... %E7%9B%B4%E5%BE%84/</a>（BGM 的鏈接判定不行……）"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/15/49/154916.jpg","floor":"#2-6","id":"1215878","time":"2017-2-25 08:35","userId":"insulsa","userName":"佛脚无影山","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Genius、小乖</span> 说: 如果运行两遍 BFS 就可以算出全 BGM 距离最为遥远的两个人。</q></div>两遍bfs要求图连通，所以只能在某个连通分量里找。最远的两个人，应该认为是从所有相互距离有限的人里边儿找。所以还是floyd-marshall，而且能用于有向图。"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/21/122188.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1215833","time":"2017-2-24 23:43","userId":"giraffe","userName":"长颈鹿","userSign":"(Happy birthday.)","message":"估计要爬好久好久<br>而且最遥远的肯定不止一个啊 一个好友也不加的人也有 那就都算咯","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/41/264146.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1215835","time":"2017-2-24 23:45","userId":"264146","userName":"小T","userSign":"(愿意给我5分钟的编辑时间吗？)","message":"小白提问：如果一个人没有任何好友，那么距离会是最远之一吗？虽然他好像没有办法被定出一个距离，所以会是论外的样子？对吗？","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/06/90690.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1215839","time":"2017-2-24 23:47","userId":"wattlebird","userName":"Genius、小乖🌟💯","userSign":"","message":"正无穷。只考虑连通图。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/30/133075.jpg","floor":"#4-2","id":"1215841","time":"2017-2-24 23:47","userId":"liaune","userName":"君寻","userSign":"","message":"如果一个人没有任何好友，那么他不在“你的世界”内，所以不在讨论范围呀"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/41/264146.jpg","floor":"#4-3","id":"1215844","time":"2017-2-24 23:49","userId":"264146","userName":"小T","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">君寻</span> 说: 如果一个人没有任何好友，那么他不在“你的世界”内，所以不在讨论范围呀</q></div>哦哦，所以说论外是对的，本来就没有算距离的必要与手段。<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">还好有在发言时一边过一下脑</span><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/58/285822.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1215836","time":"2017-2-24 23:45","userId":"rog_defwang","userName":"カナリア","userSign":"(孤独最强)","message":"都别说了，是我<a href=\